nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 134 is the 112th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 42nd published by Titan Magazines. It was released on June 12, 2012.

Creating the Hoth Battle: an exclusive interview with the assistant art director of visual effects on The Empire Strikes Back! Plus, Insider celebrates 10 years of the Republic's amazing army and a never-before-seen tale!

It was the first to release information about the fifth season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. It also covered information on the Assertor-class and Bellator-class dreadnoughts from Ansel Hsiao, as well as details for the Xolochi Dreadnought from Ian Fullwood.
